Comment: 0,0:00:00.02,0:00:00.02,Default,,0,0,0,,PART-A
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.39,0:00:04.90,Default,,0,0,0,,这全部是你亲手做的？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.31,0:00:07.40,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊  从食材处理到最后一步全都是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.15,0:00:09.32,Default,,0,0,0,,好了  你快尝尝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.82,0:00:12.15,Default,,0,0,0,,你不是要给我看你工作的样子的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.20,0:00:13.49,Default,,0,0,0,,正是  如你所见
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.53,0:00:14.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我正在工作呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.07,0:00:17.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我说…你真的是小说家吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.03,0:00:19.20,Default,,0,0,0,,别说了赶紧吃
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.54,0:00:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,这汤叫做  春妖精之全裸汤
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.83,0:00:27.84,Default,,0,0,0,,怎…怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.25,0:00:31.76,Default,,0,0,0,,超级好吃
Comment: 0,0:02:09.81,0:02:09.81,Default,,0,0,0,,PART-B
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.60,0:02:09.98,Default,,0,0,0,,多谢款待
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.10,0:02:11.31,Default,,0,0,0,,真好吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.61,0:02:13.61,Default,,0,0,0,,这都是职业作家的必备素质之一吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.98,0:02:14.44,Default,,0,0,0,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.86,0:02:17.86,Default,,0,0,0,,想亲手为意中人做菜的情感
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.61,0:02:19.49,Default,,0,0,0,,多亏了你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.78,0:02:22.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我才能充分体会到女性角色的这种感受
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.20,0:02:24.04,Default,,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.87,0:02:26.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我把写小说当成了一种游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.41,0:02:28.04,Default,,0,0,0,,但是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.58,0:02:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,不认真去玩的话  怎么可能有趣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.75,0:02:34.38,Default,,0,0,0,,正因为是游戏  所以才要全力以赴
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.80,0:02:41.89,Default,,0,0,0,,多亏了你  我可能变得更喜欢做菜了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.64,0:02:45.26,Default,,0,0,0,,好！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.64,0:02:50.19,Default,,0,0,0,,纱雾
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.73,0:02:52.56,Default,,0,0,0,,这是邻居给你的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.15,0:02:54.36,Default,,0,0,0,,邻居亲手做的菜
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.52,0:02:55.53,Default,,0,0,0,,真的很好吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.74,0:03:03.32,Default,,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.99,0:03:04.70,Default,,0,0,0,,骗子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.95,0:03:05.74,Default,,0,0,0,,唉？我吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.54,0:03:10.08,Default,,0,0,0,,这话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.87,0:03:11.42,Default,,0,0,0,,是我吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.88,0:03:13.33,Default,,0,0,0,,这个
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.50,0:03:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,好色情
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.34,0:03:18.26,Default,,0,0,0,,不是！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.30,0:03:19.38,Default,,0,0,0,,就没别的要说的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.22,0:03:25.10,Default,,0,0,0,,啊  你为什么只画贫乳的女孩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.39,0:03:28.18,Default,,0,0,0,,那  那是因为…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.56,0:03:31.44,Default,,0,0,0,,就算我提出把女主角的胸画大一点的要求
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.52,0:03:32.27,Default,,0,0,0,,你也从来不理不睬的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.94,0:03:35.02,Default,,0,0,0,,因为…的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.40,0:03:35.90,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.32,0:03:37.32,Default,,0,0,0,,因为对黄色插画
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.48,0:03:38.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我是有追求的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.99,0:03:41.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我不愿意画没有亲眼见过的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.70,0:03:43.07,Default,,0,0,0,,亲…亲眼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.95,0:03:46.53,Default,,0,0,0,,那之前的插画不会是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.21,0:03:54.96,Default,,0,0,0,,这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.92,0:03:59.13,Default,,0,0,0,,太下流了…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.13,0:04:02.09,Default,,0,0,0,,笨蛋  色魔  变态
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.26,0:04:06.05,Default,,0,0,0,,你刚刚绝对妄想了  我那超色情的画面
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.47,0:04:08.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我是为了画色情画
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.47,0:04:09.97,Default,,0,0,0,,才买了绳内裤
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.97,0:04:11.81,Default,,0,0,0,,一定觉得我很好色对吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.02,0:04:13.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我一点都不觉得！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.60,0:04:14.44,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧  还有有一点的…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.60,0:04:15.56,Default,,0,0,0,,骗人！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.65,0:04:16.73,Default,,0,0,0,,纱雾  你听好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.48,0:04:19.36,Default,,0,0,0,,一个哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.36,0:04:22.57,Default,,0,0,0,,是不会对自己的妹妹想入非非
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.45,0:04:24.99,Default,,0,0,0,,无论你有多么好色
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.41,0:04:26.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我都不会有下流的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.33,0:04:27.83,Default,,0,0,0,,更重要的是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.12,0:04:29.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我绝不会笑话你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.16,0:04:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,因为这就是哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.75,0:04:38.54,Default,,0,0,0,,像笨蛋一样…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.75,0:04:42.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我才不认识又下流又爱骗人的哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.51,0:04:43.17,Default,,0,0,0,,也不会相信你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.26,0:04:47.80,Default,,0,0,0,,那难道是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.60,0:04:50.93,Default,,0,0,0,,住在隔壁的山田小姐吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.31,0:04:55.90,Default,,0,0,0,,邻居？关系一点都不好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.61,0:04:58.27,Default,,0,0,0,,太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.36,0:05:04.11,Default,,0,0,0,,邻居亲手做的菜  真的超好吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.32,0:05:05.99,Default,,0,0,0,,大骗子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.70,0:05:08.24,Default,,0,0,0,,原来是这么一回事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.87,0:05:11.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我这几天的确总去邻居家
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.04,0:05:13.12,Default,,0,0,0,,但都是有理由的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.37,0:05:13.91,Default,,0,0,0,,有什么理由？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.29,0:05:14.91,Default,,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.08,0:05:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,现在还暂时不能说
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.63,0:05:22.38,Default,,0,0,0,,大骗子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.96,0:05:25.72,Default,,0,0,0,,一直以来  哥哥总是在骗我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.34,0:05:27.13,Default,,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.05,0:05:29.47,Default,,0,0,0,,哥哥  我讨厌你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.39,0:05:31.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我不想见到你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.14,0:05:33.60,Default,,0,0,0,,那么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.48,0:05:36.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我来证明我不是骗子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.56,0:05:38.15,Default,,0,0,0,,这一年来我一直在想
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.60,0:05:40.15,Default,,0,0,0,,怎样才能让你认可我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.19,0:05:41.32,Default,,0,0,0,,当你真正的哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.98,0:05:43.19,Default,,0,0,0,,现在我终于知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.86,0:05:44.99,Default,,0,0,0,,纱雾  我要
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.65,0:05:47.99,Default,,0,0,0,,让妹妹成为女主角
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.24,0:05:49.74,Default,,0,0,0,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.24,0:05:52.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我要写以妹妹为题材的轻小说
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.41,0:05:55.54,Default,,0,0,0,,用这世界上我最喜爱的人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.04,0:05:57.75,Default,,0,0,0,,创作出究极的轻小说
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.13,0:06:00.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我一点都不开心
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.50,0:06:01.34,Default,,0,0,0,,不会开心的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.38,0:06:03.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我才不会被这种东西扣开心扉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.84,0:06:05.42,Default,,0,0,0,,只会感到恶心
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.59,0:06:07.63,Default,,0,0,0,,哥哥大骗子  我讨厌你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.80,0:06:08.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我不会相信你的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.84,0:06:10.72,Default,,0,0,0,,你快点出去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.31,0:06:20.73,Default,,0,0,0,,下次也一起加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.11,0:06:24.86,Default,,0,0,0,,骗子…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.95,0:06:30.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我一定能成功
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.99,0:06:32.37,Default,,0,0,0,,爆发出我全部的斗志
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.91,0:06:33.83,Default,,0,0,0,,完成我能完成的事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.05,0:06:47.09,Default,,0,0,0,,又过了几天
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.72,0:06:49.80,Default,,0,0,0,,半个月一转眼就快过去了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.97,0:06:52.01,Default,,0,0,0,,从那之后
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.60,0:06:54.01,Default,,0,0,0,,我一次也没有见到过纱雾
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.10,0:06:56.81,Default,,0,0,0,,老师你好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.97,0:06:58.02,Default,,0,0,0,,请你在这周以内
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.18,0:07:00.14,Default,,0,0,0,,把新作的计划书提交上来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.77,0:07:02.48,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起  现在…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.06,0:07:04.32,Default,,0,0,0,,请给我一点时间
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.15,0:07:07.99,Default,,0,0,0,,知道了  那就请慢慢考虑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.45,0:07:11.36,Default,,0,0,0,,拒绝工作是一件很可怕的事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.95,0:07:13.12,Default,,0,0,0,,不出新作的话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.49,0:07:15.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我的位置很快就会消失
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.45,0:07:17.95,Default,,0,0,0,,甚至也会被粉丝们忘却
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.21,0:07:21.58,Default,,0,0,0,,眨眼间就会回到即便写得再多
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.17,0:07:25.38,Default,,0,0,0,,可一本都出版不了  即将崩溃的前年
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.17,0:07:29.34,Default,,0,0,0,,即便怀着这样的恐惧  我也…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.93,0:07:40.18,Default,,0,0,0,,写出好看的作品了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.85,0:07:41.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我有自信
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.98,0:07:44.48,Default,,0,0,0,,门怎么开着…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.23,0:07:46.57,Default,,0,0,0,,山田妖精老师
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.32,0:07:48.15,Default,,0,0,0,,你在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.07,0:07:50.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我自己进来了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.03,0:07:54.49,Default,,0,0,0,,妖精…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.16,0:08:02.67,Default,,0,0,0,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.88,0:08:06.21,Default,,0,0,0,,你来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.29,0:08:09.30,Default,,0,0,0,,原来约定的日子已经到了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.26,0:08:11.80,Default,,0,0,0,,你到客厅等我一下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.55,0:08:13.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.72,0:08:19.22,Default,,0,0,0,,她那么认真的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.77,0:08:20.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我还是第一次看到
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.10,0:08:22.10,Default,,0,0,0,,让你久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.73,0:08:27.02,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是我的新作品！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.19,0:08:29.98,Default,,0,0,0,,你不是说…到昨天为止连一个字都没写吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.28,0:08:30.86,Default,,0,0,0,,哼哼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.28,0:08:36.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我用能力「召唤完成原稿」将完成原稿从魔界召唤而来了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.58,0:08:39.91,Default,,0,0,0,,什…什么  居然会有这种能力…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.45,0:08:41.41,Default,,0,0,0,,…你觉得我会吃惊吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.75,0:08:43.71,Default,,0,0,0,,你直到刚才不还在拼命赶稿子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.21,0:08:48.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我才没写  就是从魔界召唤来的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.96,0:08:52.34,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你不信的话  就去看看我的笔记本吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.51,0:08:53.42,Default,,0,0,0,,你别告诉我你删了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.59,0:08:54.97,Default,,0,0,0,,就是因为要搞这无聊的小把戏
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.34,0:08:57.30,Default,,0,0,0,,山田妖精的新作…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.80,0:09:00.35,Default,,0,0,0,,呃  山田妖精就是我好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.93,0:09:01.81,Default,,0,0,0,,而目  你看
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.89,0:09:04.73,Default,,0,0,0,,原稿不就在这里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.48,0:09:06.98,Default,,0,0,0,,决一胜负吧  和泉政宗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.35,0:09:10.65,Default,,0,0,0,,我会用我的神之眼看穿你的作品
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.78,0:09:12.28,Default,,0,0,0,,正合我意  山田妖精
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.74,0:09:16.53,Default,,0,0,0,,那让我也瞧瞧你所谓从魔界召唤来的力作吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.50,0:09:25.87,Default,,0,0,0,,有趣  实在是太有趣了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.58,0:09:27.71,Default,,0,0,0,,使我的手不由自主的翻动书页
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.13,0:09:29.21,Default,,0,0,0,,使我的心不禁想要阅读下去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.88,0:09:31.88,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是动画化作家的实力吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.67,0:09:35.30,Default,,0,0,0,,而且这部作品里的女性角色全是贫乳
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.63,0:09:37.59,Default,,0,0,0,,姿势尽是情色漫画老师擅长的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.97,0:09:40.51,Default,,0,0,0,,场景和服装也都是她喜欢的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.26,0:09:41.72,Default,,0,0,0,,而且…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.06,0:09:44.18,Default,,0,0,0,,还特别的有诱惑力
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.60,0:09:46.44,Default,,0,0,0,,每一个细节构思都调整到了极限
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.98,0:09:49.52,Default,,0,0,0,,这简直就是为情色漫画老师量身打造的小说
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.19,0:09:51.23,Default,,0,0,0,,你这部…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.86,0:09:58.28,Default,,0,0,0,,这份稿子  你是认真的吗
Comment: 0,0:10:11.17,0:10:11.17,Default,,0,0,0,,PART-C
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.12,0:10:06.41,Default,,0,0,0,,到底是不是  政宗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.75,0:10:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,这对我很重要  你回答我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.38,0:10:11.38,Default,,0,0,0,,当然是认真的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.50,0:10:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.05,0:10:22.18,Default,,0,0,0,,到底什么情况
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.14,0:10:24.31,Default,,0,0,0,,…不了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.18,0:10:28.39,Default,,0,0,0,,这样的稿子  我根本贏不了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.31,0:10:30.02,Default,,0,0,0,,太恶劣了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.15,0:10:33.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我的原稿  有那么好…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.40,0:10:35.44,Default,,0,0,0,,不  我说的不是这个
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.07,0:10:38.95,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么能让我看这种东西
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.20,0:10:41.07,Default,,0,0,0,,这种…这种…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.32,0:10:44.74,Default,,0,0,0,,有那么无聊吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.24,0:10:48.08,Default,,0,0,0,,论稿子的销量  我的一定比你多一百亿倍
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.71,0:10:53.46,Default,,0,0,0,,但这根本不成胜负啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.96,0:10:56.38,Default,,0,0,0,,到底怎么了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.34,0:11:01.64,Default,,0,0,0,,这份稿子  不是为了取悦广大读者写的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.47,0:11:07.43,Default,,0,0,0,,却是为了一个人  你倾注了灵魂写成的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.60,0:11:12.81,Default,,0,0,0,,读了这份根本不能商品化的垃圾原稿
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.15,0:11:14.65,Default,,0,0,0,,内心会为之动摇的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.98,0:11:16.32,Default,,0,0,0,,在这世界上除了我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.78,0:11:19.49,Default,,0,0,0,,就只有你的妹妹情色漫画老师了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.74,0:11:21.66,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.32,0:11:24.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我都读了稿子  怎么可能会猜不到
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.78,0:11:25.28,Default,,0,0,0,,不会吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.99,0:11:31.21,Default,,0,0,0,,简直就是告诉别人  情色漫画老师是你的妹妹一样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.83,0:11:35.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我本来想把这部小说拿给妹妹看来着
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.59,0:11:38.55,Default,,0,0,0,,可以啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.01,0:11:41.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得它能非常清楚地传递你的用心
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.09,0:11:46.56,Default,,0,0,0,,通过这300页  超超超炽热的情书
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.60,0:11:53.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我还以为你有严重的暴露癖呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.15,0:11:56.15,Default,,0,0,0,,没想到你居然一点都没自觉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.69,0:11:58.19,Default,,0,0,0,,唉输了输了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.32,0:11:59.86,Default,,0,0,0,,这次是我输了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.28,0:12:01.49,Default,,0,0,0,,唉…别别…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.78,0:12:02.99,Default,,0,0,0,,你干什么呀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.20,0:12:06.03,Default,,0,0,0,,你为什么要哭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.41,0:12:08.79,Default,,0,0,0,,那样黄黄的又有趣的杰作
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.79,0:12:12.08,Default,,0,0,0,,真是谢谢你了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.92,0:12:14.83,Default,,0,0,0,,不过留下来也没有意义了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.21,0:12:16.54,Default,,0,0,0,,如果没有她的插画的话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.13,0:12:20.55,Default,,0,0,0,,话说在前头  这次是我输了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.84,0:12:22.34,Default,,0,0,0,,但并不代表你赢了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.80,0:12:23.93,Default,,0,0,0,,有什么区别吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.47,0:12:26.22,Default,,0,0,0,,所以才说你迟钝啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.26,0:12:29.35,Default,,0,0,0,,下次我会贏的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.89,0:12:33.60,Default,,0,0,0,,所以  你准备把这个怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.98,0:12:37.40,Default,,0,0,0,,你不会说不想拿给妹妹看了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.19,0:12:40.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我会的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.61,0:12:42.32,Default,,0,0,0,,况且我原先就这么打算的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.11,0:12:45.99,Default,,0,0,0,,你要干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.62,0:12:48.91,Default,,0,0,0,,你认真的吗  掉下去可不止受…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.70,0:12:53.12,Default,,0,0,0,,情色漫画老师！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.33,0:12:58.92,Default,,0,0,0,,纱雾  我这就过去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.63,0:13:00.17,Default,,0,0,0,,哥哥？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.61,0:13:25.74,Default,,0,0,0,,呃  这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.74,0:13:27.99,Default,,0,0,0,,那个  这是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.53,0:13:28.99,Default,,0,0,0,,纱雾
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.95,0:13:31.37,Default,,0,0,0,,新作的原稿完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.95,0:13:32.49,Default,,0,0,0,,你读读看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.04,0:13:38.42,Default,,0,0,0,,那个  抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.04,0:13:41.05,Default,,0,0,0,,没事  倒也算不上…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.71,0:13:44.01,Default,,0,0,0,,你为什么要做那么危险的事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.72,0:13:48.18,Default,,0,0,0,,因为你在那之后就一直不肯开门…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.01,0:13:49.64,Default,,0,0,0,,这个
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.89,0:13:50.30,Default,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.85,0:13:53.02,Default,,0,0,0,,是我暂时不开门的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.48,0:13:56.35,Default,,0,0,0,,这个是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.02,0:13:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,,战斗场景  有没有变好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.73,0:14:01.36,Default,,0,0,0,,完全变了个样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.23,0:14:02.94,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.82,0:14:05.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我看了很多格斗比赛的视频
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.20,0:14:08.07,Default,,0,0,0,,也查了许多武器的资料
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.61,0:14:09.74,Default,,0,0,0,,所以才这么…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.74,0:14:16.66,Default,,0,0,0,,但是我不喜欢有人死掉受伤的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.08,0:14:17.66,Default,,0,0,0,,这个是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.88,0:14:22.29,Default,,0,0,0,,你不要误会  我一直都是这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.00,0:14:25.38,Default,,0,0,0,,喜欢的角色死掉了我会很伤心
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.88,0:14:28.18,Default,,0,0,0,,所以一直对画这个有抵触
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.38,0:14:34.10,Default,,0,0,0,,但是  第一次和我面对面  讲述你如何创作故事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.64,0:14:37.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我就意识到  只画自己喜欢的东西是不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.10,0:14:40.27,Default,,0,0,0,,是因为我说了你画得不好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.11,0:14:43.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我实在很不甘心
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.77,0:14:45.86,Default,,0,0,0,,想着我也必须要战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.65,0:14:48.61,Default,,0,0,0,,战斗是指  和我？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.70,0:14:49.15,Default,,0,0,0,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.57,0:14:50.36,Default,,0,0,0,,也看看这个
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.57,0:14:54.20,Default,,0,0,0,,这是上色后的效果
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.24,0:14:56.91,Default,,0,0,0,,这是不同发型的版本
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.41,0:14:57.91,Default,,0,0,0,,你觉得怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.21,0:15:00.79,Default,,0,0,0,,你  能画巨乳的角色了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.33,0:15:03.92,Default,,0,0,0,,勉强达到能看的水平了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.75,0:15:05.88,Default,,0,0,0,,脱掉的话是这种感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.88,0:15:08.63,Default,,0,0,0,,感想呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.05,0:15:10.88,Default,,0,0,0,,非常色情非常棒
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.10,0:15:17.02,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗  你这半个月的时间一直在练习这个啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.39,0:15:19.98,Default,,0,0,0,,和泉老师  这样你明白了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.69,0:15:24.11,Default,,0,0,0,,你想把我从你的新作里踢出去是不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.82,0:15:27.57,Default,,0,0,0,,什么  谁说的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.03,0:15:30.07,Default,,0,0,0,,因为  你最近一直有事瞒着我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.53,0:15:32.95,Default,,0,0,0,,还和隔壁的山田小姐偷偷见面
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.37,0:15:34.24,Default,,0,0,0,,一副很开心的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.12,0:15:38.83,Default,,0,0,0,,哥哥是绝不可能在工作以外的场台认识那种女生的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.50,0:15:44.75,Default,,0,0,0,,和那女生认识以后  哥哥就变得超有干劲了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.34,0:15:49.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得  那一定就是新的插画师
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.01,0:15:52.72,Default,,0,0,0,,于是就关在房间里进行了练习
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.05,0:15:53.76,Default,,0,0,0,,纱雾…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.43,0:15:57.35,Default,,0,0,0,,听到和泉老师说要把妹妹当做女主角
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.02,0:16:00.10,Default,,0,0,0,,然后写出究极的轻小说给你看的话后
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.64,0:16:02.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我真的非常高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.56,0:16:05.65,Default,,0,0,0,,真的想为你画插画
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.03,0:16:09.86,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我绝对绝对不能输
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.32,0:16:13.11,Default,,0,0,0,,才不会把和泉老师让给那样的人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.33,0:16:18.29,Default,,0,0,0,,那是我的台词
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.79,0:16:20.83,Default,,0,0,0,,全都弄错了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.54,0:16:25.38,Default,,0,0,0,,旁边住的人其实是畅销作家山田妖精老师
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.17,0:16:27.84,Default,,0,0,0,,山田妖精老师？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.05,0:16:28.63,Default,,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.09,0:16:32.55,Default,,0,0,0,,她…她是情色漫画老师的头号粉丝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.01,0:16:34.59,Default,,0,0,0,,说想一起工作什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.39,0:16:37.18,Default,,0,0,0,,所以就变成了赌上情色漫画老师
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.72,0:16:39.47,Default,,0,0,0,,用小说来决胜负的情况
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.18,0:16:40.89,Default,,0,0,0,,那是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.02,0:16:42.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我从没听说过那样的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.73,0:16:43.89,Default,,0,0,0,,是我不想说
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.81,0:16:48.07,Default,,0,0,0,,因为害怕你可能会说
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.86,0:16:51.53,Default,,0,0,0,,比起和我你更想和畅销作家一起工作
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.95,0:16:55.57,Default,,0,0,0,,不可能的…哥哥你真是笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.91,0:16:58.08,Default,,0,0,0,,哈哈…连我自己也那么觉得
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.37,0:17:00.91,Default,,0,0,0,,结果还是不得不说
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.50,0:17:02.66,Default,,0,0,0,,不是那样…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.91,0:17:04.41,Default,,0,0,0,,那种事情…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.87,0:17:06.92,Default,,0,0,0,,呜…算了…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.46,0:17:07.88,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.29,0:17:10.71,Default,,0,0,0,,但是已经解决了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.00,0:17:11.88,Default,,0,0,0,,是我赢了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.09,0:17:14.97,Default,,0,0,0,,真厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.30,0:17:16.72,Default,,0,0,0,,竟然贏了那个人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.34,0:17:18.68,Default,,0,0,0,,和泉老师真厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.64,0:17:23.43,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然本来是想让你读了之后作决定的…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.77,0:17:24.64,Default,,0,0,0,,没那个必要
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.98,0:17:26.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我一开始就是做好了打算的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.98,0:17:31.48,Default,,0,0,0,,从今往后也请多关照  和泉老师
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.65,0:17:35.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我才是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.86,0:17:37.78,Default,,0,0,0,,请多关照  情色漫画老师
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.32,0:17:41.45,Default,,0,0,0,,人家才不认识叫那种名字的人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.87,0:17:44.04,Default,,0,0,0,,哈哈哈哈…哈哈哈…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.21,0:17:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,给我看
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.58,0:17:51.46,Default,,0,0,0,,啊…是…是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.59,0:17:52.88,Default,,0,0,0,,你在紧张些什么呀
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.38,0:17:54.55,Default,,0,0,0,,没…没紧张哦…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.76,0:17:56.47,Default,,0,0,0,,完全…一点儿都没有紧张
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.09,0:17:57.97,Default,,0,0,0,,快点
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.26,0:17:59.30,Default,,0,0,0,,哦…哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.35,0:18:01.39,Default,,0,0,0,,那…请看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.81,0:18:02.31,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.73,0:18:06.35,Default,,0,0,0,,那…我就出去了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.94,0:18:09.48,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯…不行…你坐在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.19,0:18:10.90,Default,,0,0,0,,唔…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.08,0:18:27.12,Default,,0,0,0,,不…不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.66,0:18:29.08,Default,,0,0,0,,心脏要跳破了…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.63,0:18:31.63,Default,,0,0,0,,纱…纱雾
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.34,0:18:32.92,Default,,0,0,0,,是…在！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.75,0:18:35.76,Default,,0,0,0,,怎…怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.17,0:18:37.97,Default,,0,0,0,,那…那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.18,0:18:40.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得非常好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.80,0:18:41.47,Default,,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.80,0:18:46.52,Default,,0,0,0,,只是…不能这样出成书
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.93,0:18:49.27,Default,,0,0,0,,绝对不能让别的人看
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.90,0:18:50.85,Default,,0,0,0,,太令人害羞了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.44,0:18:52.69,Default,,0,0,0,,是…是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.77,0:18:54.73,Default,,0,0,0,,果然是那样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.03,0:18:56.69,Default,,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.36,0:19:00.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.07,0:19:02.45,Default,,0,0,0,,有喜欢的人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.16,0:19:08.79,Default,,0,0,0,,是…是吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.37,0:19:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,对…这样就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.54,0:19:14.88,Default,,0,0,0,,因为我们是兄妹
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.75,0:19:18.42,Default,,0,0,0,,因为我决定了要成为她的家人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.51,0:19:22.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.60,0:20:56.02,Default,,0,0,0,,诶…那样啊  那样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.31,0:20:57.73,Default,,0,0,0,,你被甩了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.98,0:20:59.82,Default,,0,0,0,,什么啊  一脸坏笑
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.98,0:21:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,诶嘿嘿…活该
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.74,0:21:04.45,Default,,0,0,0,,然后那后来怎么样了？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.91,0:21:06.16,Default,,0,0,0,,那之后…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.37,0:21:09.28,Default,,0,0,0,,呐…纱雾
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.45,0:21:09.91,Default,,0,0,0,,哦…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.62,0:21:11.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我现在也有梦想了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.37,0:21:12.87,Default,,0,0,0,,梦想？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.08,0:21:15.67,Default,,0,0,0,,啊…对  非常大的梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.71,0:21:19.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我要把这份原稿出书
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.88,0:21:21.67,Default,,0,0,0,,这样的原稿还不够
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.96,0:21:23.55,Default,,0,0,0,,重新思考一下写份企划书
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.01,0:21:25.51,Default,,0,0,0,,然后让担当的编辑认可
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.34,0:21:27.55,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然不得到认可不行
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.84,0:21:29.39,Default,,0,0,0,,但是我一定会让它变成书的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.06,0:21:31.93,Default,,0,0,0,,让许多的人觉得它有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.31,0:21:34.77,Default,,0,0,0,,变得喜欢上主人公和女主角
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.23,0:21:36.27,Default,,0,0,0,,然后人气暴涨
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.81,0:21:39.02,Default,,0,0,0,,赚到能轻松地自立生活的钱
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.90,0:21:41.44,Default,,0,0,0,,在那之后就是动画化
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.23,0:21:44.40,Default,,0,0,0,,那就是哥哥的梦想？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.57,0:21:45.49,Default,,0,0,0,,不是不是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.70,0:21:47.03,Default,,0,0,0,,这样只是事前准备
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.36,0:21:50.03,Default,,0,0,0,,买个大屏的液晶电视放我们客厅
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.41,0:21:52.16,Default,,0,0,0,,再准备个超大的扬声器
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.83,0:21:54.83,Default,,0,0,0,,豪华的蛋糕上插上蜡烛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.58,0:21:56.92,Default,,0,0,0,,然后吧你从房间里面带出来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.33,0:21:58.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我们两个人一起看动画
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.46,0:22:01.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我写的原作  你画的插画
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.09,0:22:03.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我们两个人的动画
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.96,0:22:07.05,Default,,0,0,0,,那样的话肯定会觉得很开心的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.80,0:22:10.51,Default,,0,0,0,,悲伤的事什么的可能就会飞走哦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.22,0:22:12.72,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是我的梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.22,0:22:14.68,Default,,0,0,0,,绝对要实现的目标
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.43,0:22:17.02,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么样  厉害吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.60,0:22:19.10,Default,,0,0,0,,咳…咳…咳…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.69,0:22:21.86,Default,,0,0,0,,说太大声呛到了…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.28,0:22:26.70,Default,,0,0,0,,那样啊…这次也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.11,0:22:27.95,Default,,0,0,0,,这次也？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.92,0:22:41.54,Default,,0,0,0,,纱雾
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.17,0:22:42.71,Default,,0,0,0,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.42,0:22:45.21,Default,,0,0,0,,你从以前就是那样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.76,0:22:46.67,Default,,0,0,0,,和泉老师
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.30,0:22:51.55,Default,,0,0,0,,一直给我梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.60,0:22:54.14,Default,,0,0,0,,好  和泉老师
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.47,0:22:55.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我们就来做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.81,0:22:57.35,Default,,0,0,0,,听起来那么有趣的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.64,0:22:59.31,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么能让你一个人做呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.94,0:23:01.81,Default,,0,0,0,,那不仅仅是你一个人的梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.56,0:23:04.32,Default,,0,0,0,,让它成为我们两个人的梦想吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.95,0:23:11.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我肚子饿了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.16,0:23:14.87,Default,,0,0,0,,好好  知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.41,0:23:16.16,Default,,0,0,0,,稍微等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.50,0:23:21.50,Default,,0,0,0,,朝梦想迈出的第一步
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.00,0:23:23.75,Default,,0,0,0,,今天的事
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.63,0:23:27.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我一辈子都不会忘的吧
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Next
